  <summary date="2022-08-15T17:26:07Z" status="Introduced in House">No Tax Deductions for Workplace Harasser Buyouts Act

This bill modifies the tax deduction for trade or business expenses to deny a deduction for payments made to any employee in connection with the termination of employment if a factor in the termination was sexual assault, sexual harassment, sexual misconduct, or workplace harassment based on race, color, national origin, religion, sex, disability, or other specified factors.</summary>
